        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>The client for this project was a marketing firm that was responsible for handling the marketing efforts for large automotive companies such as Toyota and Honda. The scope of my project was to design a distributed marketing platform catered to the automotive industry. The sole focus for MVP was to design the platform to handle email and direct mail, but to also consider other distribution channels such as facebook ads, text notifications, etc., for future additions. Other features such as admin permissions, reporting, and automation were not in the scope for MVP.</p>
